    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into absolute perfection with this incredible, showroom-quality find! This vehicle is in truly mint condition, looking and driving exactly as it did when it first left the dealership. Meticulously cared for and flawlessly preserved, it\u2019s a rare opportunity for a buyer who demands the very best in automotive excellence.",
