    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant investment and labor from its next owner. The exterior shows heavy wear, including multiple deep scratches, several noticeable dents, and clear coat failure on the hood and roof. Mechanically, the engine runs but has a consistent misfire and several fluid leaks that need immediate attention. The interior has seen better days, with visible tears in the upholstery and non-functioning air conditioning. This is a project car best suited for someone with the tools and time to restore it to a roadworthy state.",
      "price": 6500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
